ed","50 g rocket salad","100 g mixed lettuce","50 g fresh baby spinach"]}],"id":"r134377","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/--nJ_n4PKFLk\/XZMuGa_jOcI\/AAAAAAAAaBQ\/7Bp3bmPdwxICd6cF8ZTceaUrMSsGCB0PACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_9ZUnp67m0wdksxq6.png","title":"Spelt Salad with Burmese Tofu","publishedAt":"2018-02-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10 g","fat":"15 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"26 g","calories":"1163 kJ \/ 278 kcal"},"usefulItems":"loaf tin (900 g\/2 lb), baking paper, cling film, serving bowl, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["The remaining tofu will keep in the fridge for <nobr>3-4 days.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","9h 10m","6 portions"]}